WEBVTT

00:00:02.706 --> 00:00:04.208
<i>[singing voice] Aniplex.</i>

00:00:08.250 --> 00:00:11.155
<i>[tense music]</i>

00:00:11.222 --> 00:00:18.069
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:00:18.136 --> 00:00:20.040
It was just a misunderstanding,
ma'am.

00:00:20.107 --> 00:00:22.044
I sincerely apologize
if we caused you

00:00:22.111 --> 00:00:23.013
any trouble just now.

00:00:23.079 --> 00:00:24.550
[gasps]

00:00:24.683 --> 00:00:25.752
[grunts]

00:00:26.185 --> 00:00:27.889
That'll do, right, Mari?

00:00:27.956 --> 00:00:31.129
Tatsuya, it really was just
a learning experience

00:00:31.195 --> 00:00:32.532
for you, right?

00:00:32.599 --> 00:00:35.237
Technically, there's nothing
in the school guidelines

00:00:35.304 --> 00:00:37.274
that prohibits students
from teaching each other,

00:00:37.341 --> 00:00:40.982
but using magic entails
some detailed restrictions.

00:00:41.517 --> 00:00:43.754
Perhaps it's best to refrain
from self‐schooling

00:00:43.821 --> 00:00:45.658
that uses magic activation.

00:00:45.725 --> 00:00:46.827
[clears throat]

00:00:47.261 --> 00:00:48.831
Because the president
herself seems

00:00:48.898 --> 00:00:50.267
to be quite inclined,

00:00:50.334 --> 00:00:52.471
I'm going to look
the other way this time,

00:00:52.539 --> 00:00:54.643
but this had better
never happen again.

00:01:00.955 --> 00:01:02.892
And what is your name?

00:01:02.959 --> 00:01:05.665
I'm Tatsuya Shiba
in class 1E.

00:01:09.038 --> 00:01:11.042
I will remember that.

00:01:13.681 --> 00:01:15.551
[Shun] Hey,
I don't owe you anything.

00:01:16.820 --> 00:01:18.724
I don't think that I
have anything over you,

00:01:18.791 --> 00:01:19.893
so don't worry.

00:01:19.960 --> 00:01:22.364
My name's Shun Morisaki.

00:01:22.431 --> 00:01:24.636
I'm part
of the main Morisaki branch,

00:01:24.703 --> 00:01:26.707
and this is not me
acknowledging you,

00:01:26.774 --> 00:01:28.109
Tatsuya Shiba!

00:01:28.511 --> 00:01:30.748
[Shun] I still say Miss Shiba
should be hanging with us.

00:01:31.850 --> 00:01:33.253
So it's like that?

00:01:33.320 --> 00:01:36.125
[Shun stammering]

00:01:38.396 --> 00:01:41.102
Hey, brother,
why don't we head on home now?

00:01:41.169 --> 00:01:42.572
Sounds good.

00:01:43.139 --> 00:01:44.241
‐ [Honoka] Um...
‐ Mm?

00:01:46.947 --> 00:01:48.183
[grunts]

00:01:53.694 --> 00:01:54.997
I'm Honoka Mitsui.

00:01:55.063 --> 00:01:56.800
I'm sorry
for what just happened.

00:01:58.269 --> 00:01:59.873
[all gasping]

00:02:00.575 --> 00:02:03.313
Thank you for covering for me.
That could've gone much worse.

00:02:03.380 --> 00:02:04.448
I know what Shun said,

00:02:04.516 --> 00:02:05.718
but it was thanks to you that

00:02:05.785 --> 00:02:08.289
the situation didn't escalate,
big brother.

00:02:08.691 --> 00:02:10.427
It's fine.
You're welcome.

00:02:11.162 --> 00:02:13.266
But please don't call me
big brother.

00:02:13.333 --> 00:02:15.103
We're both first years.
It's weird.

00:02:15.170 --> 00:02:16.507
Very well, then.

00:02:16.573 --> 00:02:18.476
What do you prefer I call you?

00:02:18.544 --> 00:02:20.581
‐ Tatsuya is fine.
‐ All right.

00:02:21.850 --> 00:02:25.357
So, um, I‐‐
I, um...

00:02:26.259 --> 00:02:27.729
You can say it.

00:02:27.796 --> 00:02:29.298
[whimpers]

00:02:29.365 --> 00:02:31.436
Do you mind if I walk
to the station with you?

00:02:33.239 --> 00:02:34.910
all: Huh?

