<i>[LiSA singing in Japanese]</i>

00:02:50.107 --> 00:02:57.221
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:03:07.307 --> 00:03:09.780
<i>♪♪ Pay attention</i>
<i>Hey what is it ♪♪</i>

00:03:09.846 --> 00:03:12.519
<i>♪♪ Watch your step now ♪♪</i>
<i>[LiSA singing in Japanese]</i>

